  s1p:[
  "On the cross, Jesus does not say “I am defeated” nor “it's over”. The Greek says <span class='g'>tetelestai</span>: accomplished, completed, settled. A craftsman's and an accountant's word: the task is carried to its end, the debt is paid.",
